<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.7.2">
<l>iṇaimali marutiṉo ṭerutiṟa vikalceytu</l>
<l>tuṇaimali mulaiyavaḷ maṇamiku kalaviyuḷ</l>
<l>maṇamali viḻaviṉo ṭaṭiyava raḷaviya</l>
<l>kaṇamali kaṇapura maṭikaḷta miṭamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The place of the god who is in splendid union of marriage</l>
<l rend="indent">with the maid with twin full breasts,</l>
<l>Having done battle with bulls so they perished</l>
<l rend="indent">along with fully entwined marutu trees,</l>
<l>Is Kaṇṇapuram full of multitudes of devotees</l>
<l>Who mingle during festivals full of affluence.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
